  "title": "Bank Operations Analyst (Account Opening) (Contract)",
  "description": "<p>Key Responsibilities:</p><ul><li>Conduct client-facing phone calls to verify and clarify onboarding information</li><li>Process new wealth client account applications, both digital and non-digital.</li><li>Review client documentation for completeness, accuracy, and compliance with AML/KYC regulations.</li><li>Guide clients through the account opening process, addressing questions or issues professionally.</li><li>Ensure onboarding procedures comply with internal policies, risk standards, and regulatory requirements.</li><li>Collaborate with internal teams to resolve discrepancies and escalate complex cases when necessary.</li><li>Support initiatives to automate or streamline the onboarding process, including using digital tools or AI-assisted platforms.</li></ul><p>Required Skills / Experience:</p><ul><li>Experience in wealth management client onboarding or high-net-worth client account opening.</li><li>Strong phone communication skills, confident in direct client interactions.</li><li>Attention to detail with the ability to accurately review and process documentation.</li><li>Exposure to digital onboarding tools or process automation is a plus.</li></ul><p><br />Interested applicants please send your resume in MS Word format and attention it to Rachel Yeo (R22104385).</p><p>Shortlisted candidates will be notified</p><p>Data provided is for recruitment purposes only</p><p>www.ambition.com.sg<br /></p><p>EA Registration Number: R22104385</p><p>Business Registration Number: 200611680D. Licence Number: 10C5117</p>",
